      <title>泰国最大上市公司股价飙升 165% 引发 CEO 和交易所会议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-04/delta-thailand-s-165-stock-surge-prompts-ceo-exchange-meeting</link>
